Quickstrike:





"Vector 9.84-1," Quickstrike replied to Dark Mouse. "Black Arachnia 
said it was in th' sountern end of th' forest. We's suppos'd t' look 
fer uh alien d'vise." He paused and transformed to beast mode. He 
sighed and briefly closed his eyes. It felt good to be out and in 
beast mode, with a mission to do.

He looked out into the forest in the distance. "Let's go t' the 
forest up there. From then on ah can map it out, then we's be off!" 
He shrugged his massive claws
